Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.28,0:00:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄黄端现 太极混沌如鸡蛋 随着\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}In the Beginning there was the darkness and then
