Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.28,0:00:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诞生了无限膨胀的时间 空间和物质 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Giving birth to endless expanding existence of time, space and matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.29,0:00:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在所见超乎我们的想象 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Now we see further than we've ever imagined
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.29,0:00:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超越了客观认知极限 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}beyond the limits of our existence
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.29,0:00:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那地方我们称之为"宇宙" \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}in the place we call:The Universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.30,0:00:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太阳是银河系亿万恒星中的一颗 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Our Sun is one of billions of stars in the Milky Way galaxy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.31,0:00:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的星系是已知宇宙中千亿 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And our galaxy is one of hundreds of billions,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.31,0:00:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能万亿星系中的一个 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}maybe trillions in the now-known universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.32,0:00:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用哈勃望远镜 我们观察到的宇宙\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}From the Hubble space telescope comes a view of the universe that was
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.32,0:00:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是穿越历史迷雾的壮丽旅行 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}a magnificent trip through the mists of history.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.32,0:00:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几乎回到宇宙大爆炸的时代 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and back, nearly all the way to the Big Bang.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.33,0:00:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一个点儿 每一个块儿\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Each smudge, each clump,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.33,0:00:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一个光子 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}each blob of light.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.33,0:01:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边繁星成千上万 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A billions stars here,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.34,0:01:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边繁星成万上千 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}a trillions stars there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.34,0:01:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想知道我们在宇宙中的位置\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}If you want to know ours place in the Universe
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.35,0:01:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来向上看 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}take a look up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.35,0:01:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那遥远 遥远的地方 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}at far, far away.
