Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.37,0:01:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的宇宙是运动的宇宙 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Ours is a universe of motion,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.37,0:01:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,膨胀的宇宙 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}expansion,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.38,0:01:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光芒的宇宙 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}light,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.38,0:01:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是昏暗的宇宙 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and blackness.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.38,0:01:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的宇宙有136亿年的历史 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We think the Universe is about 13.6 billion years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.39,0:01:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它放着作一参照 地球\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So just to put that in context, the Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.39,0:01:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和太阳系有40亿年的历史 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and Solar System is just over 4 billion years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.39,0:02:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以宇宙比地球的年龄大三倍 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So the Universe is just over 3 times older than the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.40,0:02:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在广裹无垠的虚幻的边际 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Across the vast reaches of the interstellar void,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.40,0:02:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥远的星辰彼此之间\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}distant stars are held together by the long reach
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.41,0:02:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受到引力的牵连 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of the gravity's unyielding grip.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.41,0:02:22.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些星辰经过了上百万年\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Over billions of years these stars have come together
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.42,0:02:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起形成了星系 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to form galaxies.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.42,0:02:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个星系有数千亿的星辰\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A galaxy is a collection of a hundred billions or so stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.43,0:02:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些星辰相互既不接近 也不接触\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And these stars are by no means touching each other or actually anywhere near each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.43,0:02:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和它们的体积相比 它们离的很远 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Compare their sizes they are very, very far apart from the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.44,0:02:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不通星系这东西怎么了 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The thing that blows my mind about galaxies is what monsters they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.44,0:02:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们大到不可想象 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They are incredibly huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.44,0:02:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果把太阳比作是一个句号 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}If the Sun was the size of a period on the page,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.45,0:02:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就象i 上的那一点 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the dot of an i,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.45,0:02:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的星系将是整个美国大陆\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}our galaxy would be the size continental United States.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.45,0:03:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以它们非常浩瀚 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So, they are gigantic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.46,0:03:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天文学家都知道有特殊的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Astronomers have always known there was something special
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.46,0:03:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一群星辰和太空尘\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}about the band of stars and dust.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.46,0:03:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在他们上面环绕着夜空 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that seemed encircle night sky above them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.47,0:03:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们的星系 一条白色的痕迹叫做\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It is our galaxy, a white smutch they called:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.47,0:03:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银河系 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The Milky Way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.48,0:03:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是一个光点的群体 光点\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}That band of light is the collective light
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.48,0:03:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来自成千上万颗星 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of hundreds of thousands of stars,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.48,0:03:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你用眼分不开它们 是希腊人命名的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}which you cannot see it individually with your eye and that was named by the Greeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.48,0:03:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们认为 看起来像是乳白色的河流 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They thought look like milky river so they called the Milky Way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.49,0:03:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的银河有数千亿的行星 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}There are a hundred billions stars in our galaxy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.49,0:03:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙里有数千亿个星系 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and are a hundred billions galaxies in the observable Universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.50,0:03:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在宇宙里行星的数量多于 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}That's more stars in the Universe
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.50,0:03:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球海滩上的沙粒数 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}than grains of sand on the beaches of Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.51,0:04:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果想象星系同曲棍球一样大 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}If you imagine the galaxy itself is the size of a hockey puck,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.52,0:04:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么星系彼此之间\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}then the galaxies are spaced from one to other
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.52,0:04:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有几十公分的距离 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}about few diameters apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.52,0:04:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这儿有一个球 那儿有一个球\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So there is a puck here, a puck over there,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.53,0:04:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星系在宇宙就象这样 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that's kind way the galaxies are spaced in universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.54,0:04:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从哈勃望远镜得到的图片\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Pictures from the Hubble space telescope
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.54,0:04:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展示其它星系的多样性 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}show the wide variety of alien galaxies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.55,0:04:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草帽星系 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The Sombrero galaxy,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.55,0:04:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也叫M104 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}also known as M104.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.56,0:04:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨大的星系团里最庞大的物体之一\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}One of the most massive objects in a gigantic cluster of galaxies,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.56,0:04:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草帽星系包含八千亿倍\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the Sombrero galaxy contains nearly 800 billion times
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.57,0:04:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的太阳的质量 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}as much mass as our Sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.57,0:04:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和银河系相比 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Compared to the Milky Way,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.57,0:05:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草帽星系的肚子比它的盘子大得多 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Sombrero has much large bulge relative to its highly coiled disc
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.58,0:05:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它的图片就是典型的例子 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}This image of the Sombrero galaxy it is also a prime example
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.59,0:05:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜猜看会怎样 三个世界级的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}what's happens when three of the worlds
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.59,0:05:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天文望远镜联合起来 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}top telescopes joined forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.59,0:05:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查德拉X光观察台 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The Chandra X-ray observatory,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.59,0:05:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把草帽星系发出来的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}taking an image of high power X-rays
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.60,0:05:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高能量的X光线成像 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}emitted by the Sombrero galaxy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.60,0:05:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈勃天文望远镜 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The Hubble space telescope,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.60,0:05:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉行走数百万光年的的 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}snapping an optical picture capturing the visual light,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.61,0:05:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可见光成像 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that made multimillion light year journey to the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.61,0:05:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史匹哲天文望远镜 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And the Spitzer space telescope,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.62,0:05:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用红外线成像 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}capture an infrared vision,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.62,0:05:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到草帽星系的热指纹 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}looking at Sombrero galaxy's heat signature.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.62,0:05:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三个图片结合起来 出现一个难忘的奇异景象 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Melded together this 3 images provide a staggering  and unforgettable look
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.63,0:05:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远离两千八百万光年的星系 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}at a galaxy 28 million light years away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.64,0:06:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,M51 涡状星系 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}M51, the Whirlpool galaxy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.64,0:06:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它的旋臂如棉花糖般螺旋在一起 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Its spiral arms twisting like cotton candy being spun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.65,0:06:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星系的中央聚集着恒星 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The center of the Whirlpool galaxy is so densely pack with stars,
