Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.77,0:15:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙中所有的物质和能量都在一起 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}all the mass and energy that we have at Universe would be in a single location
