Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.84,0:15:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们认为宇宙的膨胀给我们很深的启示 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We think that the expansion of the Universe is telling us something very profound.
