Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.20,0:15:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那个时刻 大爆炸之后\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}In those moment, after the Big Bang
