Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.12,0:16:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的定律中万有引力最主要 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And one of the biggest rules was the law of gravity.
