Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.93,0:16:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,密度大的部分引力吸引 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Those denser parts started gravitationally contracting
