Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.27,0:16:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般的星云的引力大 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}even more than the general cloud of gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.46,0:16:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能要上亿年 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's would take hundreds of millions years
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.29,0:16:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一个星系才形成 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}for the first galaxy to coalesce into existing.
