Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.07,0:17:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们自己的星系之谜 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}own place in the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.36,0:17:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我们想了解银河系的结构时 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}When we want to look at the structure of our galaxy
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.69,0:17:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面临的困难是我们身在其中 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the difficulty we run into is that we are inside of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.79,0:17:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只能看到从内部看到的景象 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We can only see what we can see from inside.
