Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.59,0:17:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就我们在银河系的位置 看不了多远 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and we can't see very far, from our position in our galaxy
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.42,0:17:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论那个方向都是一样 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}in many different directions.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.63,0:17:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银河系是一棒旋星系 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We think the Milky Way is a barred spiral galaxy
