Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.82,0:17:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,核厚3000光年 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}with a 3000 light year thick core.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.17,0:17:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙中的大部分星系较小 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Most galaxies in Universe are smaller.
