Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.04,0:18:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中心密度大 周边密度小 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}with a central dense core and less dense suburbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.58,0:18:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于螺旋星系 象我们的银河系\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}For spiral galaxies, like our own Milky Way
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.02,0:18:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从中心到周边的旅程\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that means a trip to visit the suburbs
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.15,0:18:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可没有象城市的高速公路 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is not unlike a trip on the freeways.
