Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.61,0:18:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们距离中心大约三万光年\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We are about 30 thousand light years away from the center
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.10,0:18:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要用2.5亿年\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and it takes us about 250 million years
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.01,0:18:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能完成这漫长的一圈 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to make one orbit around the galaxy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.50,0:18:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,群星都在自己的轨道上绕着星系转 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Now the stars are all in their orbits, all moving around the galaxy
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.09,0:18:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们看到的螺旋是如何形成的呢？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}so, what causes the beautiful spirals arms that we see?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.18,0:18:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 这儿有一种密度波 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Well, there's a sort of density wave
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.59,0:19:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在星系的这个区域 星的密度大 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and area where the stars and galaxy are just a little bit denser
