Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.11,0:19:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但密度波还在那儿 就是旋转臂 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But the density waves stays there and that's the spiral arm.
