Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.86,0:25:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某种意义上讲 这是个很好的模型\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So that's, in a sense, a good model
